Rear Window is a 1998 American made-for-television crime-drama thriller film directed by Jeff Bleckner .
The teleplay by Larry Gross and Eric Overmyer is an updated adaptation of the classic 1954 film of the same name directed by Alfred Hitchcock which was based on the short story `` It Had to Be Murder '' by Cornell Woolrich .
It was broadcast in the US by ABC on November 22 , 1998 .
This stars Christopher Reeve -LRB- in one of his final screen appearances -RRB- , Daryl Hannah , and Robert Forster .